'Yan majalisar wakilai na Wales sun ji tsoron "ta hanyar Marrets"
Akwai damuwa da wasu Majalisar Majalisar Dattijai ta Wales (AM) game da shawarar cewa an canza lakabin su zuwa MWP (Majalisar Dattijai ta Wales).
Asalin wannan jayayya yana shirin canza sunan taron zuwa "Galles Partnership".
Wasu daga cikin 'yan majalisar, daga kowane launi na siyasa, suna jin tsoron cewa wannan zai sa su zama abin kunya.
A AM ma'aikaci ya ce kungiyar tana da damuwa game da "mai zaɓi tare da Twp da Pwp".
Ga masu karatu ba Wales: a cikin yaren Wales, "twp" yana nufin "audiote" da pwp yana nufin "sallama."
A AM daga Plaid ya ce kungiyar a cikin duniyarsa "ba ta yi farin ciki ba" kuma ya bayar da shawarar madadin.
Wani majalisar wakilai mai kiyayewa ya ce kungiyar tana da "buɗewa" game da canza sunan, amma ya nuna cewa zaɓin MWP yana kusa da Muppet (Marreta).
A cikin wannan mahallin, haruffa w a Wales tana da kalmomi kamar haruffa ko a Turanci na Yorkshire.
Hukumar ta majalisar, a halin yanzu tana tsara dokoki don shigar da canje-canje na suna, ta ce: "Manufar karshe game da yadda ake nada Majalisar Majalisar za a dauki nasu."
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales na 2017 ta ba da iko ga taron don canza suna.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta wallafa sakamakon tattaunawa na jama'a game da shawarwarin, wanda ya rubuta goyon baya na gaba ɗaya ga shawarar nada taron "Majalisar Galles".
Game da batun lakabin AM, hukumar ta fi son "Majalisar Majalisar Wales", ko WMP, amma zaɓin MWP ya fi dacewa a cikin tattaunawa na jama'a.
A bayyane yake, AMs suna bayar da shawarar madadin, amma ƙoƙarin hadu da amincewa na iya zama ciwon kai ga Shugaban kasa, Elin Jones, wanda ya kamata ya gabatar da tsarin doka game da canje-canje a cikin 'yan makonni.
Dokar game da gyare-gyare za ta hada da wasu canje-canje dangane da yadda taron ke gudanar da ayyukansu, kamar dokoki game da rashin cancantar AM da kuma saitin tsarin kwamitoci.
Lokacin da suka yi jayayya da dokar, AMs za su sami ƙarshen magana game da batun yadda za a zabi.
