Sainsbury's shirin shiga kasuwar kwaskwarima ta Birtaniya
Sainsbury's yana gudana tare da Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams tare da sassan kwaikwayo a cikin manyan wuraren shakatawa, waɗanda masu tallafawa suka tallafawa.
