Almanac: Mai kirkiro na Geiger Counter
Kuma yanzu wani shafi na mu Almanac "Sunday Morning": A ranar 30 ga Satumba, 1882, yau ne shekaru 136 da kuma ci gaba da Contar ...An haife Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger lissafi na gaba a Jamus.
Geiger ya ci gaba da wata hanya don gano da kuma auna radioactivity, ƙirƙirar da ta kawo ƙarshen kai ga na'urar da aka sani da Geiger Counter.
