Lokacin da muke sanya wannan belun kunne, za mu iya jin sakamakon atoms da aka saki ta rediyo a cikin ma'adinai. "
Evans: "Duba, yanzu yana cikewa!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a 1945, 'yan kwanaki kafin ranar haihuwarsa 63.
Amma ƙirƙirar da ya bayar da sunansa har yanzu yana ci gaba.
Sabuwar rigakafin cutar kansa yana koyar da tsarin rigakafi don "duba" kwayoyin cutarwa
Sabuwar rigakafin kansa yana koyar da tsarin rigakafi don "duba" kwayoyin cutarwa da kashe su
rigakafin ya koyar da tsarin rigakafi don gane kwayoyin cutarwa a matsayin wani ɓangare na magani
Hanyar ta haɗa da cire kwayoyin rigakafi na mai haƙuri da canji a cikin lab
Wadannan kwayoyin, waɗanda zasu iya "duba" protein na yau da kullum ga yawancin ciwon daji, sannan an sake allurar su a cikin jiki
Gwajin gwaji yana samar da sakamako mai ban sha'awa a cikin marasa lafiya da ke dauke da cututtuka masu yawa.
Wata mace da aka magance da allurar rigakafin, wanda ke koyar da tsarin rigakafi don gane kwayoyin cuta, ta ga kansa a cikin mahaifa ya ɓace fiye da watanni 18.
Hanyar ta ƙunshi cire kwayoyin rigakafi daga mai haƙuri da canjinsa a cikin lab don su sami "duba" protein na yau da kullun ga yawancin ciwon daji, wanda aka kira da HER2. Ana sake allurar waɗannan kwayoyin a cikin jiki.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky, daga Cibiyar Cutar Kankara ta Amurka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Sakamakonmu na nuna cewa muna da allurar rigakafi mai ban sha'awa."
HER2 "yana kula da haɓaka nau'ikan daban-daban na ciwon daji", ciki har da na mahaifiyar, ovarium, huhu, da kuma launin launi, in ji Farfesa Berzofsky.
Hanyar kama da cire kwayoyin rigakafi daga marasa lafiya da "koyar da su" don kaiwa kwayoyin ciwon daji ta yi aiki a maganin wani nau'in leukemia.
