HIV/AIDS: China ta ruwaito karuwar 14% sabon lokuta
China ta sanar da kashi 14 cikin dari a yawan mutanenta da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS.
Sama da mutane 820,000 sun sha wahala a kasar, in ji hukumomin tsaro.
An sanar da kusan 40,000 sababbin lokuta kawai a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018.
Yawancin sababbin lokuta sun haifar da watsa shirye-shirye ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ke nuna canji game da baya.
Yawancin lokaci, HIV ya yadu da sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin sakamakon cutar jini.
Duk da haka, adadin mutanen da ke fama da cutar ta wannan hanyar ya rage zuwa kusan kashi ɗaya, hukumomin tsaro na kasar Sin sun ce a cikin taron a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, dangane da bambanci na shekara-shekara, yawan wadanda ke rayuwa da cutar HIV da AIDS a kasar Sin ya karu a 100,000 mutane.
Ciyar da HIV ta hanyar jima'i matsala ce mai tsanani a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An kawar da jima'i a kasar Sin a 1997, amma an ce nuna bambanci a kan al'ummar LGBT yana da yawa.
Nazarin sun yi la'akari da cewa, saboda adadin rikice-rikice na kasar, 70 zuwa 90% na maza waɗanda suka yi jima'i da wasu maza sun auri mata.
Yawancin watsa shirye-shiryen cututtuka sun fito ne daga kariyar jima'i da ba ta dace ba a cikin wannan dangantaka.
