Jihohi goma sha takwas da Columbia District sun goyi bayan jayayya da sabon mafaka siyasa
Jihohi goma sha takwas da Columbia District suna goyon bayansu ga rikici na doka na sabon manufofin Amurka wanda ke ki amincewa da mafaka ga wadanda suka tsere daga cin zarafin kungiyoyi ko gida.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da gundumar sun aika da amincewa da curiae (abokan kotun) a ranar Jumma'a a Washington, don tallafawa wani neman mafaka wanda ke jayayya da wannan manufar, ya ce NBC News.
Cikakken sunan mai gunaguni a cikin hukuncin Grace vs. Sessions cewa American Civil Liberties Union ta tsaya a watan Agusta kan siyasa ba a bayyana ba.
Mutumin ya ce abokin tarayyarsa "da 'ya'yanta,' yan ƙungiyar ta'addanci" sun yi ta, amma hukumomin Amurka sun ƙi neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
An tsare shi a Texas.
Ma'aikatan jama'a da ke tallafawa Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, waɗanda ke samar da adadin masu neman mafaka a Amurka, a matsayin al'ummomin da ke fuskantar matsaloli masu yawa tare da ƙungiyoyi da cin zarafin gida.
Sabuwar mafaka na Amurka ta soke wani yanke shawara na 2014 daga Majalisar Resources na Baƙi wanda ya ba da damar baƙi ba tare da takardun gudun hijira ba daga tashin hankali na gida idan sun nemi mafaka.
Mai gabatar da kara a Colombia, Karl Racine, ya ce, a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Jumma'a, cewa sabuwar manufofin "ba ta yi watsi da shekaru goma na dokoki na jihohi, na tarayya da na kasa da kasa ba."
"Dokar tarayya ta bukaci a bincika duk buƙatun mafaka bisa ga abubuwan da ke faruwa da su; wannan haramtacciyar ta keta wannan ka'idar," an karanta a cikin sanarwar amicus curiae.
Har ila yau, lauyoyi sun yi jayayya a cikin wannan jawabin cewa haramtacciyar 'yan sanda ta shiga baƙi ta shafi tattalin arzikin Amurka, yana mai cewa su ne mafi yiwuwa su zama masu kasuwanci da kuma "samar da aikin da ake bukata."
Mahukunta Jeff Sessions ya umarci alƙalai na hijira su daina barin mafaka ga wadanda suka tsere daga cin zarafin gida da ƙungiyoyi a watan Yuni.
"Mafaka yana samuwa ga waɗanda suka bar ƙasar saboda tsanantawa ko tsoron dangane da kabilanci, addini, kabilanci ko mallakar wani rukuni na musamman na zamantakewa ko tare da wani ra'ayi na siyasa," in ji Sessions a sanarwar da siyasa a ranar 11 ga Yuni.
Mafaka ba ta da nufin sauƙaƙe duk matsaloli, ba duk matsaloli masu tsanani ba, wanda mutane suna fuskantar kowace rana a dukan duniya.
