"Mutane sun ce ya kasance mai girma, gaskiya ne.
Amma zai iya kasancewa mafi girma, musamman a tsakanin masu zabe marasa yanke shawara a yankunan lardin da kuma matasa masu zabe, daga 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda, ko da yake ba su son shugaban kasa ba, sau da yawa ba su zabe ba. "
Har ila yau, kafin shaidar jama'a na Ford ya bayyana zargin da ake yi na cin zarafin jima'i da aka nada a kotun Koli, masu tattaunawa sun ba da shawarar cewa za a iya faruwa da mummunar martani idan 'yan Republicans sun ci gaba da tabbatarwa.
"Wannan ya zama kuskure ga Jam'iyyar Republican," in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican na kasa a farkon mako da ya gabata, in ji NBC News.
"Ba kawai game da zabe na kwamitin ba, ko kuma ko Kavanaugh zai dauki matsayinsa na alƙali. Yana kuma game da yadda 'yan Republicans suka bi da batun da kuma yadda suka bi da shi," in ji Guy Cecil, mai kula da Priorities USA, wani rukuni da ke taimakawa zaɓen dimokiradiyya, zuwa tashar labarai.
Duk da haka, Amirkawa suna da alama wani abu da aka raba game da wanda ya gaskata bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, tare da ƙananan mafi yawan daidaitawa da farko.
Wani sabon bincike na YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41% na masu bincike sun yi imani da cikakken shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35% sun ce sun yi imani da cikakken ko kuma sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, 38% sun ce sun yi imanin cewa Kavanaugh yana yiwuwa ko ya yi ƙarya a kan shaidarsa, yayin da kashi 30% kawai suka tabbatar da hakan game da Ford.
Bayan ba da shawarar Flake, FBI ya fara bincike game da zargin Ford, da kuma wani mai zargin, Deborah Ramirez, a cewar Guardian.
Ford ya yi rantsuwa a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai a mako da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya damu da ita ta jima'i yayin shan giya lokacin da take da shekaru 17.
Ramirez ya yi ikirarin cewa kotun da aka nada a babban kotun ta bayyana nau'in jinsi a lokacin da su biyun suka halarci biki a lokacin da suka yi karatu a Yale a cikin shekarun 1980.
Mai kirkiro na World Wide Web yana son ƙirƙirar sabon Intanet don gasa tare da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, mai kirkiro na World Wide Web, ya kirkiro farawa wanda ke so ya yi hamayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
The latest project wannan almara hali na fasaha, da Inrupt, ne wani kamfanin da ya yi amfani da bude code-source dandali daga Berners-Lee, da Solid.
Wannan yana ba masu amfani damar yanke shawara inda aka adana bayanai da kuma wanda ke da damar samun damar samun bayanai.
A cikin wata hira da aka yi wa Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya fada cikin farin ciki cewa manufar da ke karkashin Inrupt ita ce "mallakar duniya."
"Dole ne mu yi haka yanzu," in ji shi game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi."
A aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasaha na Solid don ba da damar mutane su kirkiro kansu "makarantar bayanan sirri ta kan layi", ko POD.
Wannan zai iya ƙunshe da lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyuka, kalandar, music library da sauran sirri da kuma sana'a kayan aiki.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna samuwa a cikin browser guda ɗaya kuma a lokaci guda.
Abin da yake musamman game da bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne cewa kawai mai amfani zai iya yanke shawara game da wanda yana da damar zuwa wane irin bayanai.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "kamar sirri ta hanyar bayanai".
Ra'ayin Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, shine samar da albarkatu, tsari da ƙwarewa masu dacewa don taimakawa wajen samar da Solid available ga kowa.
Kamfanin a halin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, dandamali na tsaro wanda IBM ta sayi, wasu masu shirye-shirye na ciki da aka yi amfani da su don aiki a kan shirin da kuma al'umma masu shirye-shirye.
A farkon wannan makon, masu ƙirƙirar fasahar da aka yada a duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen kansu ta amfani da kayan aikin da ake samu a shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su magana da "Facebook da Google game da gabatarwa ko ba a cikakken canji inda duk kasuwanci model suna juya daga rana zuwa wata.
"Ba mu nemi izni daga gare su ba."
A cikin sakon da aka wallafa a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "aikin Inrupt shine ƙirƙirar makamashi na kasuwanci da tsarin muhalli wanda ke taimakawa wajen kare aminci da ingancin sabon yanar gizo wanda aka kirkiro tare da Solid."
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza yanar gizo lokacin da ya kirkiro Consortium na World Wide Web a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin watannin da suka gabata, Berners-Lee ya kasance murya mai tasiri a muhawara game da tsaka-tsaki na Intanet.
Kodayake yayin da aka gabatar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa kafa da kuma shugaba na World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation da Open Data Institute.
"Ina matukar tattaunawa tare da wannan zamanin yanar gizo na gaba," in ji Berners-Lee.
