Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley ya ji "ƙananan" game da jima'i
Tom Daley ya ce ya girma ya zama ƙasa da kowa saboda jima'i, amma wannan ya ba shi dalili don samun nasara.
'Yan wasan tseren shekaru 24 sun ce ba su lura ba har sai sun shiga makarantar sakandare cewa "Dukkansu kamar ni ne."
A cikin tattaunawa na farko Desert Island Discs na Radio 4 da Lauren Laverne ya gabatar, ya ce an bayyana 'yancin jima'i don ba da "tsammanin" ga wasu.
Ya kuma ce ya zama uba ya damu da ya kasa lashe Olympics.
Mai gabatarwa na yau da kullum na shirin, Kirsty Young, ya dauki hutu na watanni da yawa saboda rashin lafiya.
Da yake bayyana a matsayin mai baƙi a shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya ce ya ji "ƙananan" ga kowa saboda "ba ya dace da soyayya da yara da yara ba."
A cikin kalmominsa, "A yau, mun ji muna da ƙananan daban-daban shine dalilin da ya sa ya ba ni iko da ƙarfi don cimma nasara."
Manufarsu ita ce tabbatar da cewa "wani mutum", ya ce, kada kowa ya kunyata lokacin da suka gano jima'i da sauri ko daga baya.
The biyu Olympic tagulla lambar yabo ya zama m LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da rabo a Commonwealth Wasanni a wannan shekara a Australia don kiran karin kasashe don kawar da laifin jima'i.
A bayyane yake, ya bayyana shi saboda ya ji farin ciki ya iya rayuwa a buɗewa ba tare da sakamako ba kuma ya yi niyyar ba da "tsammanin" ga wasu.
The World Tricamper ya ce yana ƙaunar mutum, dan wasan kwaikwayo na Amurka Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu a shekarar 2013, "ya yi mamakin ni."
Daley ya yi aure a shekarar da ta gabata tare da wanda ya lashe Oscar, tsohuwar shekaru 20, kodayake ya ce bambancin shekaru ba shi da wata matsala.
"Lokacin da muka wuce haka lokacin da muke matasa" - shi na farko a wasannin Olympics yana da shekaru 14 kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka, ya ce, yana da wuya a sami wani daga wannan shekaru wanda ya wuce sama da ƙasa irin wannan.
Ma'aurata suna da ɗa a shekarar da ta gabata a watan Yuni, mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ya ce "dukan hangen nesa" sun canza.
"Idan na tambaye ni a shekarar da ta gabata, duk abin da yake da muhimmanci shi ne "samun wani lambar zinariya," in ji shi.
"Amma ka sani? Akwai abubuwa mafi girma fiye da Olympics zinariya lambobin.
Madadin zinariya na Olympics shine Robbie. "
Ɗansa yana da sunan ɗaya da mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekarar 2011 yana da shekaru 40 bayan an gano shi da ciwon daji a cikin kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda ya mutu ba kuma ɗaya daga cikin abubuwan da ya tambaye shi ya kasance idan sun kasance suna da tikitin zuwa gasar London a 2012, saboda yana so ya kasance a gefen gaba.
Ya ce, "Ba za ku ce ba, ba za ku zo nan ba, sa'an nan ma'aikatan farko na uba."
"Na kasance yana riƙe da hannunsa ba lokacin da ya daina numfashi, kuma ya kasance kawai lokacin da ya daina numfashi sosai kuma ya mutu, a ƙarshe na gane cewa ba shi da iyakancewa," in ji shi.
A shekara ta biyu, Daley ya fafata a wasannin Olympics na 2012 kuma ya sami lambar tagulla.
"Ya kasance cikakke sanin cewa shi ne abin da ya yi mafarki dukan rayuwa: zubar a gaban mutane da yawa a cikin Olympics ... babu mafi kyau ji," in ji.
Dukan wannan kuma shine wahayi na zaɓin waƙa na farko - girman kai, na Heather Small - wanda aka gano shi a lokacin shirye-shirye don gasar wasanni, kuma har yanzu yana ba shi fata na kaza.
