Rashin software ya kasance musamman muhimmanci, tun lokacin da Baden-Wuerttemberg aji jiragen ruwa za a gudanar da wani tawagar na kimanin 120 jiragen ruwa, kawai rabin da ake buƙata a cikin tsofaffin Bremen aji Fragatas.
Har ila yau, an san cewa jirgin ruwa yana da nauyi sosai, wanda ke rage aikinsa kuma yana iyakance damar jiragen ruwa don shigar da ƙarin ayyuka a nan gaba.
An yi imanin cewa "Rheinland-Pfalz" na 7000 ton, yana da nauyi sau biyu na jiragen ruwa masu kama da nau'i-nau'i waɗanda Jamus ke amfani da su a yakin duniya na biyu.
Baya ga hardware kuskure, farashin dukan aikin ciki har da kafa tawagar, shi ma ya zama matsala.
