An sabunta bayanai game da Mare Red Mare: Mayar da hankali a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
A cewar sabon bayani daga Florida Fish and Wildlife Commission, rage yawan Mare Red Mares a wasu yankunan Tampa Bay.
FWC ta ba da rahoton cewa an gano yanayi na ƙarancin raguwa a yankunan yankin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier, wanda ke ba da shawarar raguwa.
Kwayar Mare Red ta fadada kusan kilomita 201 a gefen teku, daga yankin Pinellas zuwa arewa zuwa yankin Lee zuwa kudu.
Za a iya samun ƙuƙwalwa a kusa da 16 km a bakin teku na Hillsborough County, amma a ƙasa da yankuna fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga Mare Red Mare a yankin Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an rubuta matsakaicin mayar da hankali a kusa da ko a bakin teku na Pinella, ƙananan mayar da hankali zuwa high a kan Hillsborough County County County, babban mayar da hankali a cikin Manatee County, babban mayar da hankali a kusa da ko a kasa na Sarasota County County.
Har ila yau akwai rahotanni game da numfashi a cikin jihohin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
A makon da ya gabata, babu rahotanni game da cutar numfashi a yankin arewa maso yammacin Florida.
